After running `flutter create`, add the following line INSIDE the `<manifest>`
element (above `<application>`) in android/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:

    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.READ_SMS"/>

Final manifest top should look like:

    <manifest xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android">
        <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.READ_SMS"/>
        <application ...>
            ...
        </application>
    </manifest>
